Zoe McLellan https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Zoe_McLellan 0 Zoe McLellan (born November 6, 1974) is an American television actress, known for her roles as Petty Officer Jennifer Coates in the CBS procedural JAG, as Lisa George in the ABC comedy-drama soap Dirty Sexy Money, and as Meredith Brody in the CBS series NCIS: New Orleans (2014–2016). Recently, she starred in the role of Kendra Daynes in the ABC political drama Designated Survivor.
